# ~/.config dotfiles — ignore browser profiles, app state and anything with secrets.
# These dirs hold cookies, saved passwords, caches and gigabytes of model/cache blobs.

# Browser profiles (cookies, Login Data, caches, on-device model blobs)
google-chrome/
chromium/
BraveSoftware/
microsoft-edge/
opera/
vivaldi/
mozilla/

# App state / potential credentials
Docker Desktop/
docker-secrets-engine/
navicat/
evolution/

# Runtime state, not real config
pulse/
ibus/

# Generic caches / volatile state (defensive)
**/Cache/
**/Code Cache/
**/GPUCache/
**/GraphiteDawnCache/
**/DawnGraphiteCache/
**/DawnWebGPUCache/
**/Service Worker/
**/IndexedDB/
**/*Cache*/
**/Cookies
**/Cookies-journal
**/*.log
**/*.ldb
